  "slug": "in-medias-res-arid-articulations",
  "title": "In Medias Res — Arid Articulations",
  "summary": "Ellie Pritts’ work combines a mix of AI and analog video to culminate in a meditation-qua-colorscape of Joshua Tree’s Martian-like desertscapes.\nUtilizing analog video in their  explorations of place and identity (California, United States), “Arid Articulations” is Pritts’  newest series capturing the martian landscapes of the Mojave desert. Long known for their surrealist photography of Joshua Tree National Park, this is Pritts’ first video series exploring these themes with modular video synthesis, circuit bent (glitched) video and AI-collaborative animations.",
